enriched_requirements.full_sentence:
Chapter IV shall be complied with in addition to the instructions /
regulations of respective regulators such as SEBI, IRDAI and PFRDA, as
applicable;

(2) There shall be a Board approved policy encompassing the model of
insurance distribution to be adopted, issues of customer appropriateness,
suitability, and grievance redressal;

It shall also be ensured that no incentive (cash or non-cash) is
paid to the staff engaged in insurance broking / corporate agency services
by the insurance company;

Further, the repeal of these directions, instructions, or guidelines shall not in any
way prejudicially affect:
